Package com.sanyavertolet.interview.data.value

Class DoubleValue

java.lang.Object
com.sanyavertolet.interview.data.value.Value
com.sanyavertolet.interview.data.value.DoubleValue
public final class DoubleValue extends Value
A final class representing a double value in an expression. The DoubleValue class extends the Value class and provides specific implementations for handling arithmetic operations, comparisons, and conversions involving double values.
